{"title":"Buying a bike from a bike shop vs buying online","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/buying-a-bike-from-a-bike-shop-vs-buying-online/","date":1613646240000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=45&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2400,1598 2400w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1920,1278 1920w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/DSC_4342-5fff9b5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-619979 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"Chevin Cycles, Otley – bike shop\" title=\"Chevin Cycles, Otley – bike shop\" />                                            <p class=\"firstpara\">When buying a bike, in addition to figuring out <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-bike/\">what type of bike you want</a>, there’s also the question of whether you buy from a bike shop or online.</p>\n<p>Back in the day, you simply went to a bike shop, tried out a couple bikes and off you went. But in the mid-90s, everything started getting shaken up by this confusing, maybe-too-good-to-be-true thing called the internet.</p>\n<p>Ever since, buying products online has become an increasingly popular option, whether that’s from an online retailer or direct-sales bike brand. It’s not hard to see why, with the ease of shopping at home, seemingly lower prices and delivery right to your door.</p>\n<p>But what are the pros and cons of buying a bike at your local bike shop versus buying online, and what route should you take?</p>\n<h2>Buying at the local bike shop – pros and cons</h2>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (1597 / 2400));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"ima