o.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1110 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1480 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1110 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1480 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-620008 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/AM10394-1-c5da084.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Wheelbase bike shop, Ilkley\" title=\"Wheelbase Ilkley\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Bike shops are normally tied to a select number of brands.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Allan McKenzie / SWPix.com </i></span></div>\n<p>Knowledge and fit are the biggest advantages of buying from an actual, physical shop.</p>\n<p>Good bike shops live and breathe bikes so their advice might clue you in on something you didn’t know and they can help you make sure the bike’s size is correct.</p>\n<p>Getting the right <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/sizing-and-fit/\">bike fit</a> is dependent on a variety of factors: height, flexibility, leg and arm length, riding style, even personal preference. There’s little that can compare to actually riding the bike and having a trained eye there to look at you and analyse the bike fit.</p>\n<p>Geometry can also vary significantly from one bike to another, which in turn has a knock-on impact on fit and handling, so a good bike shop can help advise on the intricacies of <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/sizing-and-fit/road-bike-geometry-explained/\">road bike geometry</a> and <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/the-ultimate-guide-to-bike-geometry-and-handling/\">mountain bike geometry</a>.</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/sizing-and-fit/road-bike-sizing/\">Road bike size guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/sizing-and-fit/mountain-bike-sizing-what-size-bike-do-i-need/\">Mountain bike size guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/womens-bike-sizes-a-simple-guide/\">Women’s bike size guide</a></li>\n</ul><div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (772 / 1200));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10364-6141647.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C193, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10364-6141647.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C386 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10364-6141647.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C579 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10364-6141647.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C772 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source 