e/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1860%2C1238 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C814 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1632%2C1086 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C814 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1632%2C1086 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1110 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1480 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1110 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1480 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-619981 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/AM10352-33cda98.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Bike shop workshop servicing – Wheelbase, Ilkley\" title=\"Bike shop workshop servicing – Wheelbase, Ilkley\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> You’ll miss your local bike shop’s workshop when it’s gone.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Allan McKenzie / SWPix.com</i></span></div>\n<p>Some shops have pivoted to offering services beyond simply buying a bike, including quality coffee, in-depth bike fitting and coaching. Many bike shops also organise group rides or have a club.</p>\n<p>Beyond price, the other negative is that, unfortunately, really good bike shops stocked with the inventory you desire can be quite rare, and most bike shops are tied to the brands they specifically stock.</p>\n<p>Unfortunately a lot of bike shops are started by people with passion, rather than business savvy, and employee turnover can be high, due to low wages and long hours, too.</p>\n<p>However, if your local bike shop is run by passionate, knowledgeable staff, and stocks brands that work for you, then that personal touch can be very valuable as a customer.</p>\n<h2>Buying online – pros and cons</h2>\n<p>Buying a bike online can be done in two ways. First, there are manufacturers, such as <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/canyon/\">Canyon</a>, <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/yt/\">YT</a> and others, that ship bikes straight to customers. Direct-sales brands, as they’re known, typically have a team in each country for technical and warranty support.</p>\n<p>Then there are online shops with their own bike brands, including <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/vitus/\">Vitus</a> from Chain Reaction Cycles, and <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/ribble/\">Ribble</a>. You’ll also find some sites with exclusive deals with certain manufacturers, with those bikes only being available from that retailer (exclusive partnerships).</p>\n<p>Whether it’s the direct-to-consumer model or an online site blowing out last year’s frames, the number-one benefit to buying online is price. Simply put, there are fewer layers to the end purchase, so less margin has to be made. This results in a nicer bike for less money or stretching your budget up a level in components.</p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-94