h: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-435771 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/03/YT-Jeffsy-CF-29-Pro-02-943423e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"YT Jeffsy CF 29 Pro full suspension mountain bike in white\" title=\"YT Jeffsy CF 29 Pro\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Direct-sales brands such as YT normally offer excellent value for money.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Dan Milner / BikeRadar</i></span></div>\n<p>Sounds awesome, doesn’t it? Well, there are downsides to buying a bike from the comfort of your own home.</p>\n<p>Unless you snag a ride on a demo day or have a friend with the bike you want, you’re spending a significant amount of money without a test ride. This, of course, can be less of an issue if you know what numbers you need on a geometry chart.</p>\n<p>The savings you were so stoked on might not be there in the end, either.</p>\n<p>On a basic level, you will have to <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/workshop/workshop-bike-assembly/\">assemble your bike from the box</a> when it arrives and, if the bike shows up with a kinked cable, the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/workshop/how-to-bleed-shimano-disc-brakes/\">disc brakes need to be bled,</a> or the wheel got tweaked in transit, that’s extra time and money to get those issues resolved.</p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=898%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1198%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2017/08/Canyon-bike-box-52876a8.jpg?qual